snippet.title: Formula for the Volume of a Sphere: Video III (Tanton: Mathematics)
snippet.description: In this third video of "geometry formulas explained" we show how Archimede's deduced found the volume of a sphere. To do so he had to use a formula for the volume of a cone (which we derive in video II).
